title: Haubiversum
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, International, Italian, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A cafe/bakery with a diverse and large variety of different kinds of food, including clearly labeled vegan items. Breakfast is served until 3:00 pm; a vegan breakfast, for example, could be warm sweet couscous, soy yogurt with amaranth and tofu. Sells regional and seasonal eco-labeled rolls, regional vegan juices, soy milk, soy yogurt, vegan hot chocolate, coffee and more.
